body:
## Steps to reproduce the issue

The following module generates an error when parsed with Yosys built at head.

yosys -p 'read_verilog -sv scratch.sv;'

module Module();
  int a;
  int b;

  always_comb begin
    a = f1();
  end

  function int f1();
    f1 = f2();
  endfunction

  function int f2();
    f2 = b;
  endfunction

endmodule

## Expected behavior

Parses without errors

## Actual behavior

examples/scratch.sv:14: ERROR: Non-constant expression in constant function
examples/scratch.sv:10.10-10.12: ... called from here. X
